{"tid":2354303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國展開大規模新冠疫苗接種　紐約一名護士率先接種　","createTime":"2021-01-05T11:18:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T13:23:49.000Z","uid":366655,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7405739dfdb341b3d8520076150f84484cda7132","tid":2354303,"uid":366655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T11:18:59.000Z","msg":"美國正式展開大規模新型冠狀病毒疫苗接種工作，紐約長島一間醫院的一名深切治療部護士，成為首位接種疫苗的人。這名護士形容充滿希望。紐約州州長葛謨說，隧道盡頭見到曙光，但仍有漫長的路要走。<br />\n<br />\n總統特朗普在社交網站Twitter貼文，指首劑疫苗已經接種，恭喜美國，恭喜世界。<br />\n<br />\n領導疫苗計劃的首席顧問斯拉維說，已經確保首批290萬劑疫苗，可以在3日內分發，有信心疫苗落在合適的人手上，如果分發或接種過程存在問題，亦可以很快調整過來。他又預計，到明年3月中旬，將會有足夠劑量的疫苗，供應給1億名美國人，當中大部分會是高危群組，明年5月底或6月中，大部分美國人應該可以獲接種。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/09ae51r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F09ae51r.jpg&h=b51506b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">點解第一個打嘅唔係亞洲人<br />\n點解個醫生唔係亞洲人<br />\n根本係歧視亞洲人</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565274-20201214.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565274-20201214.htm&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAGxURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=af57dd2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565274-20201214.htm&h=71a24d76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565274-20201214.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8341d0824d24619936821a865cf0f455218f4af0","tid":2354303,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T11:19:50.000Z","msg":"唔係話vaxx係侵既就唔打咩？"},{"pid":"ba8e592759c02ab6882c9c9630ed4f1b8ad41c42","tid":2354303,"uid":16057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T11:22:49.000Z","msg":"BLM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmo